COIN COLLECTOR.

> PROEJCT V0.3
    THIS PROEJCT IS OPEN SOURCE, YOU CAN FEEL FREE TO MODIFY IT
    
    !FONT LICENSE -font/OFL.txt
    !UNDER MIT LICENSE
> MADE WITH
    SDL2 - for the GAME
    SDL2 TTF - for the FONT
    gcc - c compiler
    c - for PERFORMANCE

> INSTRUCTIONS
    - THIS WAS MADE IN LINUX -
        SO YOU'LL NEED SDL2.dll IN THE SAME FOLDER AS THE EXE LIVES
    - RUN -
        'make run'
    - MODIFY THE MAKEFILE -

    - LINUX -
        gcc src/main.c src/Entity.c src/Text.c src/Game.c -Iinc -o bin/app.exe -lSDL2 -lSDL2_ttf
    
    - WINDOWS -
        gcc src/main.c src/Entity.c src/Text.c src/Game.c -Iinc -o bin/app.exe -I<where sdl2 include> -L<where SDL2 lib> -lSDL2 -lSDL2_ttf
